blockedPageDontAskAgain.message: Don't ask again; always use this browser

blockedPageSecureBrowserExplanation.message: HP Sure Click Secure Browser helps protect your PC from websites and files infected with malware, ransomware or viruses.

blockedPageSecureV2.description: Button to open the website in a secure web browser.

contextMenuOpenSecure.description: Context menu item to open a link in a secure web browser.

extDescription.message: Safe internet browsing with HP Sure Click Secure Browsing.

optionsClearAllRememberedDecisionButton.description: Button to forget all decisions remembered by the extension.

optionsClearRememberedDecisionsButton.description: Button to forget a single decision remembered by the extension.

optionsNoRememberedDecisions.description: Message displayed on the settings page when there are no saved preferences to view.

optionsPromptDisabled.description: Message displayed on the settings page when there are no settings the user can view.
optionsPromptDisabled.message: There are no settings to modify with your configuration.

optionsTrustedOriginsTitle.description: Title for a list of URLs which are remembered to always open in the default browser.

optionsUntrustedOriginsTitle.description: Title for a list of URLs which are remembered to always open in a secure web browser.

popupClearRememberedDecisionsButton.description: Button to forget all decisions remembered by the extension.

popupClearRememberedDecisionsText.description: Message explaining that popupClearRememberedDecisionsButton forgets all decisions remembered by the extension.
popupClearRememberedDecisionsText.message: HP Sure Click Secure Browsing remembers which sites you have chosen to access safely using the HP Sure Click Secure Browser and which sites you have chosen to open using the default browser. Click the button below to clear these choices.

popupDontAskAgain.description: Message displayed when the user has told the extension not to ask again and to always use this browser.
popupDontAskAgain.message: You have chosen to open all sites in this browser.

popupGenericError.description:
Message displayed when there is an unknown error. The '
' marks a new line.
popupGenericError.message:
HP Sure Click has encountered an error.
Please restart the browser.

popupHelpLinkText.description: Text which links to the help page.

popupInitRequired.description: Message displayed when the product requires initialization.

popupIs32bitFirefox.description: Message displayed when an incompatible version of Firefox is installed.
popupIs32bitFirefox.message: This extension does not support 32-bit Firefox. Please install 64-bit Firefox.

popupMissingHelper.description: Message displayed when there is an error because the product is not installed.
popupMissingHelper.message: The extension cannot connect to HP Sure Click. Please check that a compatible version of HP Sure Click has been installed and is running.

popupNoError.description: Message displayed when there are no errors.
popupNoError.message: You are being protected by HP Sure Click.

popupOpenOptionsPageButton.description: Button to open the settings page.

popupOpenOptionsPageText.description: Message explaining that popupOpenOptionsPageText opens the settings page.
popupOpenOptionsPageText.message: HP Sure Click Secure Browsing remembers which sites you have chosen to access safely using the HP Sure Click Secure Browser and which sites you have chosen to open using the default browser. Click the button below to open the settings page.

popupProductDisabled.description: Message displayed when the whole product (not just the extension) is disabled.

popupSBXDisabled.description:
Message displayed when the extension is not enabled by configuration. The '
' marks a new line.
popupSBXDisabled.message:
This extension has been disabled.
Please contact your system administrator.

popupUnconfigured.description: Message displayed to a consumer customer when the product is unlicensed.
popupUnconfigured.message: HP Sure Click is awaiting configuration and has been disabled.

popupUnlicensed.description: Message displayed to an enterprise customer when the product is unlicensed.
popupUnlicensed.message: HP Sure Click is unlicensed and has been disabled.
